WEBVTT

00:05:30.461 --> 00:05:32.819
Wote tunafanya hili mara kadhaa kwa siku,

00:05:32.843 --> 00:05:36.487
lakini hatutambui jukumu la kutazama
na kuona linavyofanya kazi

00:05:36.511 --> 00:05:38.090
katika matendo yote,

00:05:38.114 --> 00:05:41.778
na namna gani maarifa ya uono yanavyoweza
kuboresha kila kitu.

00:05:42.625 --> 00:05:45.321
Karibuni, nilipata kundi la
wataalamu wa kupinga ugaidi

00:05:45.321 --> 00:05:47.274
katika makumbusho mbele ya huu mchoro.

00:05:47.298 --> 00:05:50.728
mchoro wa El Greco, "Utakasaji wa Hekalu,"

00:05:50.752 --> 00:05:54.839
ambapo Kristo, katikati, katika ishara
ya kupangusa na yenye vurugu,

00:05:54.863 --> 00:05:57.770
anawafukuza watenda dhambi kutoka
katika hekalu la maombi.

00:05:58.321 --> 00:06:01.932
Kundi la wapambana na ugaidi walikuwa
na dakika tano katika mchoro ule,